$BR $BR
Does the equation have real solutions? Input Yes or No: \{ans_rule(5) \}
$BR $BR 
If your answer is Yes, input the solutions:
$BR
\( x_1 = \) \{ans_rule(20) \} and \( x_2 = \) \{ans_rule(20) \} 
with \(x_1\le x_2\).
$BR
EOT

$ans0 = "No";
$ans1 = "";
$ans2 = "";
ANS(str_cmp($ans0));
ANS(str_cmp($ans1));
ANS(str_cmp($ans2));

